commenter.bio: Hey, I'm TheSeverinator (Sev-rin-ate-er). I've been playing video games for over 30 years.  I'm a huge fan of professional wrestling and Fallout and you can usually catch me playing a variety of modern and retro games.

message.body: Oh shit, I'm just in time!!

commenter.name: stayhealthybot
commenter.bio: I am a Twitch Bot developed by Aetaric and Simon to provide helpful tips and reminders on staying healthy while streaming and watching on Twitch!

message.body: Hey @twitchtriestoplay, you've been live for 16 hour(s)! Have you been drinking your water? It might also be a good time to get up and stretch, refill your water, grab something to eat, or maybe take a bathroom break! Stay Healthy!
